{"tid":2021084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"<香港發生修例風波>中央廣播電視總台推出專題片《另一個香港》","createTime":"2020-05-17T13:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T13:58:48.000Z","uid":59309,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32bca98ed232a2db7a1779656e2e342d0a370f16","tid":2021084,"uid":59309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"<strong>中央廣播電視總台推出專題片《另一個香港》，探尋修例風波背後的真相。</strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年，香港發生修例風波，激進暴力犯罪行為嚴重踐踏法治和社會秩序，嚴重破壞香港繁榮穩定，嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」原則底線。<br />\n<br />\n專題片《另一個香港》通過現場實錄、香港民眾的聲音及各國專家的評論，聚焦「黑色風暴」籠罩下的香港，抽絲剝繭，一探修例風波背後的原因。<br />\n<br />\n第一集《香港之亂》記錄香港修例風波以來爆發的暴力和破壞活動，講述身處漩渦中的人物故事；第二集《風從何來》分析亂局原因，還原事實真相，看看「港獨」分子和反華勢力如何以「反修例」為由，將香港推向危險邊緣的實際用心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.cctv.com/2020/05/17/ARTIot7yvFNbaiBeO6fGxFo3200517.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.cctv.com%2F2020%2F05%2F17%2FARTIot7yvFNbaiBeO6fGxFo3200517.shtml&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=964cdd70\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.cctv.com/2020/05/17/ARTIot7yvFNbaiBeO6fGxFo3200517.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"092dbcc520e4690c358590c966127fb3907e38de","tid":2021084,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"你好人好姐鬼得閒反你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d5bca8cca7426ac4ebe9d0b066c150ffbea934","tid":2021084,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"想睇下佢點吹外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa4fe3acbd1cd7b4020e02527ae584e32431933","tid":2021084,"uid":97398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"咪又有美帝亡我之心不死，配合港英餘孽同地產霸權鼓動年輕人上街"},{"pid":"44fd4c7f097af2c2154a357e5579676a359263d9","tid":2021084,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"[戰略分析]香城ONLINE 527添馬之戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2015261\" da